description:
Sorry, I skipped the after party for this one because the audio quality was exceptionally bad. There was lot's of echoing, squeals, quiet people, and SethBling's infamous rage typing.

It is "Redstoners" versus "Mine Inc.". This is the Quarter Finals (Game #2 of 4) for Reddit's: Fellowship of the Wool, RFW tournament. 16 Teams of 4 Players are competing against each other. The sets are 1 game each, so if you lose you are out of the tournament.

(Warning: *Spoiler!*)
Match Ups: http://www.bracketmaker.com/tmenu.cfm?tid=415112

The goal is to collect all 3 different wools and place them on your victory monument before the other team. These wool are very difficult to get. You are not allowed to use dyes on wool, you are not allowed to enter the void area between the 2 lanes, and there many other rules as well.

Team: Redstoners
SethBling: http://www.youtube.com/user/sethbling
FVDisco: http://www.youtube.com/user/FVDisco
